data.description: Step into this well maintained home and instantly fall in love. This home features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The family room off the open kitchen would be ideal place to cuddle up in front of the fireplace on the cozy fall nights ahead. Upstairs you'll the secondary bedrooms along with the primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings and ensuite bath. The primary bathroom features dual sinks paired with shower and separate garden tub. The backyard is a nice size with a covered patio for the summer bbqs. Home has received recent updates such as interior and exterior paint, recent HVAC update, kitchen cabinet updates, etc. Located minutes from the AT&T Stadium, Rangers Stadium, Arlington Highlands with tons of shopping and dining, and Grand Prairie's Epic Central district there's always something to fun to do for everyone. This great home won't last long. Reach out to schedule your tour today.
